    public interface ServiceRef
extends org.opendaylight.yangtools.yang.binding.DataObject
    Type of references to a particular service instance. This type can be used when defining module configuration to refer to a particular service instance. Containers using this grouping should not define anything else. The run-time implementation is expected to inject a reference to the service as the value of the container.

    This class represents the following YANG schema fragment defined in module config
    (Source path: META-INF/yang/config.yang): 

     grouping service-ref {
     leaf type {
         type service-type-ref;
     }
     leaf name {
         type leafref;
     }
 }
    The schema path to identify an instance is config/service-ref
